{"builtWith":"0.15.15","comments":[{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":"               // hydrogen // schema // motion // effects // color // exposure"},{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":" | Exposure — Photographic exposure adjustment."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Industry Standard"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Mirrors AE's Exposure effect with photographic controls:"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Exposure**: Measured in f-stops. Each stop doubles/halves brightness."},{"LineComment":" |   +1 stop = 2× brighter, -1 stop = 0.5× brighter."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Offset**: Adds a constant to all pixel values. Primarily affects"},{"LineComment":" |   shadows and midtones. Used to adjust black point."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Gamma Correction**: Power function adjustment. Values < 1.0 brighten"},{"LineComment":" |   midtones, values > 1.0 darken midtones."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Properties (All Animatable)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | | Property | Type | Min | Max | Behavior | Default |"},{"LineComment":" | |----------|------|-----|-----|----------|---------|"},{"LineComment":" | | exposure | Number | -20.0 | 20.0 | clamps | 0.0 |"},{"LineComment":" | | offset | Number | -10.0 | 10.0 | clamps | 0.0 |"},{"LineComment":" | | gammaCorrection | Number | 0.01 | 10.0 | clamps | 1.0 |"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Mathematical Model"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | For each pixel:"},{"LineComment":" | 1. Apply exposure: `pixel * pow(2.0, exposure)`"},{"LineComment":" | 2. Apply offset: `pixel + offset`"},{"LineComment":" | 3. Apply gamma: `pow(pixel, gammaCorrection)`"}],"decls":[{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[0,0],"start":[0,0]}},"bindType":"NonRec","expression":{"abstr